An Act relating to The Oklahoma Real Estate License
7
Code; amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 858-303B, which
8
relates to accounting of expenditure for services;
8
authorizing certain negotiations in advance of
9
certain services; requiring certain disclosure of
9
information pertaining to compensation and fees;
10
prohibiting requirement of certain agreement to show
10
