BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13
14
SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 858-303B, is
14
15
amended to read as follows:
15
16
Section 858-303B. Any A. A real estate broker or agent may
16
17
negotiate compensation and fees with the represented party in
17
18
advance of the services provided. A real estate broker shall
18
19
disclose any information pertaining to compensation and fees
19
20
including, but not limited to, the party responsible for payment and
20
21
amount of each payment for each transaction to the represented party
21
22
in advance of the services provided.
22
23
B. A real estate broker or agent who charges and collects any
23
24
fees in advance of the services provided by the broker shall provide
24
