person for whom services are performed for, but no longer than one
4
5
(1) year from date of contract for such services.
5
6
C. A real estate broker or agent shall not be required to
6
7
procure a buyer broker showing agreement or contract agreement prior
7
8
to showing real estate.
8
9
SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
